comments.body:
@jmccormick2001 Thanks for your report. If this is really exactly the same Podman version, that’s certainly unexpected.

Can you upload and collect debug logs from both builds, please (`podman --log-level=debug bud …` or the like) ?

Another thing to test would be whether it is the platform that matters, or whether the manifest changes on repeated uploads; e.g. try using the same host and build+push the same image twice in a row and see whether that impacts the manifest (this is not a _known_ impact of https://github.com/containers/image/issues/733 but it looks a bit similar).
